      "id": 1,
      "text": "The Davis House, built in the 1750s, is Coram’s oldest surviving structure and earned a spot on the National Register of Historic Places.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
